Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can finally intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaiju {\i0}appearing in a world\Nweakens the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's early for two at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Knight! Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That's my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 7: What's Our Reason\Nfor Coming Together?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Episode 7: What's Our Reason\Nfor Coming Together?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a {\i1}kaiju{\i0}, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,—Gridknight Storm!\N—Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Onija, let me take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chill! Just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, let's withdraw for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can beat Gauma this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a waste to lose this {\i1}kaiju{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It saved us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god it's not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Where'd it go?!\NThis ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Now it's all beat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And to think they entrusted\NDynazenon to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koyomi! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Let's look for the {\i1}kaiju{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys search from above.\NIt couldn't have gotten far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. I've gotta fix it somehow.\NWe can't fight like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not seeing the {\i1}kaiju{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I wasn't watching my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just keep an eye on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"It's time to change capitals\Nif Tokyo's like this."\N"Another rampaging {\i1}kaiju{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this purple guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. Was that giant a {\i1}kaiju{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure, but I couldn't control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We made another enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to make enemies\Nwhen you change things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our {\i1}kaiju {\i0}was pretty strong.\NIf we play it right, we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly pumped up.\NSomething happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're pissed\N'cuz that guy hugged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Looks like Mujina's\Ngot a cute side—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just taking responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Arata. Uh, my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She always talks about you, Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You've known her since middle school,\Nright? Was she always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You work nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You could say that.\NI... help people in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, uh, Tachibana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?! Anyone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauma sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like shit right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}kaiju{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No use. Couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving. Let's grab something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier... For teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you being serious\Nfor a change ain't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't fight to settle\Npersonal grudges, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of {\i1}kaiju{\i0}\Nisn't for killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for killing humanity as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't always get\Nthe things you guys say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll go along with it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better! Now we're pumped\Nand ready to roll, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, there you are! I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mean thing to say\Nto a comrade in arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Where's Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell knows? He ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? On his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and hope he comes back quick.\NWe'll be up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? All night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for the {\i1}kaiju{\i0}.\NWhat about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell my parents I'm staying\Nat a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're working well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saved by this purple guy?\NIs he a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, he picked a fight right after.\NWhat's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,—Minam—\N—Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Koyomi! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, don't worry me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's all? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your atrocious fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Atrocious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Knight, please don't be\Nso rude right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Gridknight Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the name's not important though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We protect the world\Nfrom the threat of {\i1}kaiju{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the world... from {\i1}kaiju{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that purple guy involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean, you become that?\NYou transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Talk about fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that red guy was\Na {\i1}kaiju{\i0}, but I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ragtag crew got wrecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, Dynazenon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon. That's its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Did you come to fight {\i1}kaiju{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Which is why\Nwe want to cooperate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! And speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can use this Fixer—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are shady as hell.\NThey roll up on us out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not work with the wounded.\NYou'll only hold me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it? You wanna cooperate with us,\Nor are you picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Knight... For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with them?\NGet on the same page first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that smart, Gauma? Dynazenon's broken,\Nso shouldn't we fight together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon. When {\i1}kaiju {\i0}appear\Nin a world, so does opposition—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,like antibodies that rise to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But it seems pretty obvious\Nthat they're not bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to make sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't heal with time after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I went to save someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A person I think I hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody once told me something:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's best to live honestly\Nwith your feelings."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the same person\Nyou're searching for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who lived\Nin a world I couldn't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A total beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who entrusted\NDynazenon to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Authorized Personnel Only"\N"DO NOT ENTER"\N"Japan Expressway"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Gauma plans to do.\NWe can't exactly fight {\i1}kaiju {\i0}like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You always carry that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hot? Maybe I'll go buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This... It was Kano's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to play with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano! Can I try it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When Kano...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When my sister and I were little,\Nwe got along just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But before long, we grew apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at home, I hardly saw her smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I saw her in that video\Nsmiling and having fun in chorus club,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it kinda surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one time she invited me\Nto her recital, she was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, maybe she wanted to\Nget along again like we had in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was the last time I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kano was really bullied...\NIf she really committed suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she smiled at me that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I know nothing about Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still don't know\Nif it was suicide or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know why she was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep investigating more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was just a stranger to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She was your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If she was a part of you,\Nshe's not some stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a runny nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It's a snotty mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get us some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I'll come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Mujina? Need a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I don't get tired\Nwhen connected to {\i1}kaiju{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Real {\i1}kaiju {\i0}users don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the {\i1}kaiju{\i0}. Dynazenon's not\Nin good shape, but we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle—!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon! This time,\Nwe're gonna whoop your ragtag ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ragtag crew got wrecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?! Being ragtag\Nis what brought us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not sure about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong. It wasn't to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Knight Bursting Light Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Something Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}kaiju{\i0}'s stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Knight, I'll use Fixer Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? We only have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm using it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon! It's time to\Nget your power back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can fight to our heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two of them and two of us!\NThere's no excuse to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! We won't be beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gridknight Circular!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dyna Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,—Big Blade Strike!\N—Knight Circular End!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for the irregular, we had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Irregulars come because of {\i1}kaiju{\i0}.\NIt's a good omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time... Next time,\Nwe'll do even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved our asses! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Knight. Gridknight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And me, I'm the Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Second?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta say thanks\Nfor healing Dynazenon—!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your hands to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Until next time, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! It's this late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry. We might make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Access Mode... Dyna Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"For Kisarazu Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"For Kisarazu Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you saved him! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It helped us realize we should\Nvalue each other more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much! Until now, I didn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come along if I\Nlook into Kano some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find this person—Futaba Senda.
